---
title: Sticky Sesame Chicken with Noodles
description: Honey and soy are two flavours that were made for each other. Sweet, sticky, and with a kick of heat, the delicious sauce in this recipes guaranteed to take your stir-fry game to new levels of greatness. Quick, easy and bursting with fresh flavours and good-for-you ingredients, this is a great quick fix recipe if you're a little short on time. Don't forget to slurp those noodles!
